{"tid":698090,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食鬼妹?其實唔難","createTime":"2018-06-11T11:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T15:47:53.000Z","uid":151003,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0972959dd2146b9143e6ed7b02913672783d4f","tid":698090,"uid":151003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"見到有巴打食美國&rdquo;milf&rdquo;咁多人留名, 咁我都開心share下<br />\n<br />\n細佬我土生土長&rdquo;舊&rdquo;香港人,<br />\n早年有幸到海外留學,<br />\n年間食到不少世界各地美女,<br />\n依家&rdquo;學有所成&rdquo;, 想分享一下心得<br />\n<br />\n首先當然唔少得學好英文,<br />\n口音唔太重要,<br />\n最緊要清楚,有自信<br />\n係英語國家生活既巴打唔多唔少都有著數<br />\n<br />\n第二,幽默感都好重要,<br />\n好多時亞洲人會比人定為好死板,唔識玩,唔識笑<br />\n其實可以扮下小丑🤡,講d爛笑話.<br />\n<br />\n第三, 要吹得水,<br />\n搞笑還搞笑,當你搞完笑,講野都要有內容,<br />\n內容方面就睇你強項係咩<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野其實唔關你英文好唔好,<br />\n好多人就算母語係英文都會講1/2句就dead air<br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得達哥如果英文好d應該殺死唔少女女<br />\n<br />\n以上個幾點其實都要時間同心機練習<br />\n小弟想當年都係cs1.6小毒男一個,<br />\n估唔自己會變得咁快<br />\n<br />\n點識? <br />\n現代主流西方社交文化都離唔開, party, club, bar. <br />\n當然其他地方都會識到,但係無咁多. <br />\n<br />\n其實好多鬼妹,一開始都唔係好接受到亞洲人,<br />\n當然有一部分k pop fans除外 (但係呢一d通常都有少少怪)<br />\n重點係你要比對方感覺到其實你同鬼佬唔係想象中差咁遠 (生/心理上) 其實有好多第一世界國家比較鄉下地方既人以為香港係日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然Sexual racism一定存在, 唔係個個都接受到<br />\n有聽過&rdquo;would rather black than Asian&rdquo;. <br />\n<br />\n好似講左好多啊媽係女人既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗到再寫<br />\n<br />\n細佬我試過milf,不過肉體上都係鐘意18-25<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n費事無圖齋吹<br />\n去玩識既北歐3x歲女女(走肥唔該)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <em> <a href=\"https://image.ibb.co/iEOa58/8_FCB7_BA0_D280_44_B4_8_F4_C_C98_B24_C2176_D.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FiEOa58%2F8_FCB7_BA0_D280_44_B4_8_F4_C_C98_B24_C2176_D.png&d=2bBJuoEnBYSyeseD%2BhNa%2Bi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=1d563956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://image.ibb.co/iEOa58/8_FCB7_BA0_D280_44_B4_8_F4_C_C98_B24_C2176_D.png</a></em><em> <a href=\"https://image.ibb.co/bTjRCo/7272_BCA6_9_DC4_4385_8_F1_D_D54897_A4430_F.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FbTjRCo%2F7272_BCA6_9_DC4_4385_8_F1_D_D54897_A4430_F.png&d=2bBJuoEnBYSyeseD%2BhNa%2Bi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=50838e63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://image.ibb.co/bTjRCo/7272_BCA6_9_DC4_4385_8_F1_D_D54897_A4430_F.png</a></em>"},{"pid":"ae2b75195948d1ec04585a69cc60d091979831a5","tid":698090,"uid":151003,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T12:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/iEOa58/8_FCB7_BA0_D280_44_B4_8_F4_C_C98_B24_C2176_D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FiEOa58%2F8_FCB7_BA0_D280_44_B4_8_F4_C_C98_B24_C2176_D.png&h=14c6133d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/bTjRCo/7272_BCA6_9_DC4_4385_8_F1_D_D54897_A4430_F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.ibb.co%2FbTjRCo%2F7272_BCA6_9_DC4_4385_8_F1_D_D54897_A4430_F.png&h=49d75d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貼錯"},{"pid":"cc2e394095ca5cb2a4da9bf77450758cb914d4c9","tid":698090,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:29:50.000Z","msg":"去邊先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d92025c597b89840b137fed5165bbd654c04c1","tid":698090,"uid":141917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T22:01:49.000Z","msg":"高質post"},{"pid":"a555fda37efb9dbf2d4ce76b716d75161b9c7280","tid":698090,"uid":138860,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":