 will really notice a change if you do this for 30mina day for 6months. Perhaps pick one (UK/US) to start with first. Otherwise you will likely end up with a bizarre hybrid of different accents. <br />\n<br />\nAfter you have built the basics, you should really work how to keep a conversation going. This is a skill that will take some time to master. 🙏"},{"pid":"1d0b8c1ab82f7bba003c38c6b8051349d8c24451","tid":698090,"uid":151003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd582ee7c3681e46ef63c64dc90098cfc463689d","tid":698090,"uid":26522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T11:33:55.000Z","msg":"但唔係long stay好難食到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T11:41:43.000Z","msg":"好彩既話,一晚ko (clubbing)<br />\n有朋友試(洋腸)過一晩2round<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5847fa4dba39df676c4a38f38c26b233698b0163","tid":698090,"uid":26522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d0b8c1ab82f7bba003c38c6b8051349d8c24451","tid":698090,"uid":151003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cd582ee7c3681e46ef63c64dc90098cfc463689d","tid":698090,"uid":26522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T11:33:55.000Z","msg":"但唔係long stay好難食到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T11:41:43.000Z","msg":"好彩既話,一晚ko (clubbing)<br />\n有朋友試(洋腸)過一晩2round<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T11:44:23.000Z","msg":"其實外國應該易食啲，係心理關口"},{"pid":"b232f3db4c7e4abc0018c225cf5a5faf299e46f2","tid":698090,"uid":82082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T11:49:36.000Z","msg":"巴打幾歲？"},{"pid":"1ef642dbe9eaac00b6b98e4bfc7cc98be9b90713","tid":698090,"uid":151003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b232f3db4c7e4abc0018c225cf5a5faf299e46f2","tid":698090,"uid":82082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T11:49:36.000Z","msg":"巴打幾歲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T11:50:15.000Z","msg":"2尾